quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  49,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  49,1,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, Allah aur is ke rasool ke agay paish qadmi nah karo aur Allah se daro, Allah sab kuch suneney aur jan-nay wala hai"
  49,2,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, apni aawaz NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki aawaz se buland nah karo, aur nah NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ke sath onche aawaz se baat kya karo jis terhan tum aapas mein aik dosray se karte ho, kahin aisa nah ho ke tumhara kya karaya sab ghaarat ho jaye aur tumhe khabar bhi nah ho"
  49,3,"jo log rasool khuda ke huzoor baat karte hue apni aawaz pust rakhtay hain woh Dur haqeeqat wohi log hain jin ke dilon ko Allah ne taqwa ke liye jaanch liya hai, unn ke liye mughfirat hai aur ajar azeem"
  49,4,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, jo log tumhe hujron ke bahar se pkarte hain un mein se aksar be aqal hain"
  49,5,"agar woh tumahray bar aamad honay taq sabr karte to unhi ke liye behtar tha, Allah dar guzar karne wala aur Raheem hai"
  49,6,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, agar koi fasik tumahray paas koi khabar le kar aeye to tahaqeeq kar liya karo, kahin aisa nah ho ke tum kisi giroh ko na danista nuqsaan pouncha betho aur phir apne kiye par pasheman ho"
  49,7,"khoob jaan rakho ke tumahray darmain Allah ka rasool mojood hai agar woh bohat se mamlaat mein tumhari baat maan liya kere to tum khud hi mushkilaat mein mubtala ho jao magar Allah ne tum ko imaan ki mohabbat di aur is ko tumahray liye dil pasand bana diya, aur kufar o fisq aur nafarmani se tum ko mutnafar kar diya"
  49,8,aisay hi log Allah ke fazl o ahsaan se raast ro hain aur Allah Aleem o hakeem hai
  49,9,aur agar ahal imaan mein se do giroh aapas mein lar jayen to un ke darmain sulah karao phir agar un mein se aik giroh dosray giroh se zayad-ti kere to zayad-ti karne walay se lrho yahan taq ke woh Allah ke hukum ki taraf palat aeye phir agar woh palat aeye to un ke darmain Adal ke sath sulah kara do aur insaaf karo ke Allah insaaf karne walon ko pasand karta hai
  49,10,"momin to aik dosray ke bhai hain, lehaza apne bhaiyon ke darmain taluqaat ko durust karo aur Allah se daro, umeed hai ke tum par reham kya jaye ga"
  49,11,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, nah mard dosray mardon ka mazaq arhayin, ho sakta hai ke woh un se behtar hon, aur nah aurtain doosri aurton ka mazaq arhayin, ho sakta hai ke woh un se behtar hon aapas mein aik dosray par ta'an nah karo aur nah aik dosray ko buray alqab se yaad karo imaan laane ke baad fisq mein naam peda karna bohat buri baat hai jo log is rawish se baz nah ayen wohi zalim hain"
  49,12,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, bohat gumaan karne se parhaiz karo ke baaz gumaan gunah hotay hain tajassus nah karo aur tum mein se koi kisi ki gheebat nah kere kya tumahray andar koi aisa hai jo apne marey hue bhai ka gosht khana pasand kere ga? dekho, tum khud is se ghinn khatay ho Allah se daro, Allah bara tauba qubool karne wala aur Raheem hai"
  49,13,"logo, hum ne tum ko aik mard aur aik aurat se peda kya aur phir tumhari qoumain aur bradryan bana den taakay tum aik dosray ko pehchano Dur haqeeqat Allah ke nazdeek tum mein sab se ziyada izzat wala woh hai jo tumahray andar sab se ziyada parhaiz gaar hai yaqeenan Allah sab kuch jan-nay wala aur bakhabar hai"
  49,14,"yeh badwi kehte hain ke"" hum imaan laaye"" inn se kaho, tum imaan nahi laaye, balkay yun kaho ke"" hum Mutee ho gay"" imaan abhi tumahray dilon mein daakhil nahi howa hai agar tum Allah aur is ke rasool ki farmaa bardari ikhtiyar kar lau to woh tumahray aamaal ke ajar mein koi kami nah kere ga, yaqeenan Allah bara Dur guzar karne wala aur Raheem hai"
  49,15,haqeeqat mein to momin woh hain jo Allah aur uss ke rasool par imaan laaye phir unhon ne koi shak nah kya aur apni jaanun aur malon se Allah ki raah mein jehaad kya wohi sachey log hain
  49,16,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn ( mudaiyaan imaan ) se kaho, kya tum Allah ko apne deen ki ittila day rahay ho? halaank Allah zameen aur asmano ki har cheez ko jaanta hai aur woh har shai ka ilm rakhta hai"
  49,17,"yeh log tum par ahsaan jatate hain ke unhon ne islam qubool kar liya inn se kaho apne islam ka ahsaan mujh par nah rakho, balkay Allah tum par apna ahsaan rakhta hai ke is ne tumhe imaan ki hadaayat di agar tum waqai apne dawa-ayimaan mein sachey ho"
  49,18,Allah zameen aur asmano ki har posheeda cheez ka ilm rakhta hai aur jo kuch tum karte ho woh sab is ki nigah mein hai
